PrecisTransfer to the Province of MANITOBA, of all interests in a parcel of land situate next to Riding Mountain National Park in the Local Government District of PARK, Manitoba, that contains an area of some 0.603 hectares, which is to be used for the widening and improvement of a provincial highway.
